description: This Chainlink VRF common Anurak purrs with a rating of 5, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 15, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, Nine Lives for East, 2 for South, and 2 for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/20053-59223-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Anurak [15 Votes, Common]
